(20, 1, 'Cùng dự đoán giá bán Galaxy S23 5G: Liệu tương lai sẽ rẻ hơn các bản tiền nhiệm để tiếp cận người dùng?', '1638712984_4.jpg', '<h2 style=\"margin: 20px auto; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, \'DejaVu Sans\', \'Liberation Sans\', Freesans, sans-serif; color: #333333; outline: none; zoom: 1; width: 600px;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: #288ad6; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 18px; outline: none; zoom: 1;\" title=\"Samsung\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/samsung\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"Samsung\">Samsung</a> vẫn chưa ra mắt dòng <a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: #288ad6; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 18px; outline: none; zoom: 1;\" title=\"Galaxy S22\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/samsung-galaxy-s22\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"Galaxy S22\">Galaxy S22</a> nhưng hiện tại đã có những rò rỉ ban đầu về <a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: #288ad6; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 18px; outline: none; zoom: 1;\" title=\"s23 5g\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/dtdd/samsung-galaxy-s23-5g\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" type=\"s23 5g\">Galaxy S23 5G</a>. Bên cạnh cấu hình thì mức giá của <a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; color: #288ad6; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 18px; outline: none; zoom: 1;\" title=\"Smartphone\" href=\